'''minge'''
# ''British, slang'' [[vagina]], [[pudenda]]
[[Category:Slang]]

'''Collapsed minge'''. The Collapsed Minge phenomenon first originated on www.oasisforum.com in 2003 when forum user Daniel Muhammed El-Hadj Crook, otherwise known as 'Stocky' posted a picture of a grandmother, naked, seemingly impersonating ex-Stone Roses singer Ian Brown. This was in response to the late ex-Forum Admin James' excessive censorship of the forum, together with his henchmen DSGoddard (now a dentist), and Fenster (who today works as a traffic warden). 

Her ''minge'' was in a particularly ragged state, and looked somewhat worse for wear, and as she was standing up it looked like it had collapsed, hence the term collapsed minge.

Tragically, noone (not even Horizon or Monkey Tennis!) saved the picture, and the pictures were lost to the world forever.